data.description: AMAZING DEAL for a great home nestled in the sought-after GOOSE CREEK ISD offering the perfect combination of potential & location. As you approach the property, you're greeted by an inviting front porch. Stepping inside, you'll find an open floor plan that promises endless possibilities for customization. The kitchen boasts tons of cabinets & countertop space. With some personal touches & modern upgrades, this space can be transformed into the heart of the home, inspiring delicious meals and unforgettable memories. With two large living areas—one downstairs and another upstairs—you'll have ample space for gatherings or a potential entertainment zone. With the primary bedroom downstairs & 4 more generously sized bedrooms upstairs, every member of the household will have a tranquil retreat. The appeal of this property extends to the outdoor space, as a large backyard invites you to create your private oasis. Don't miss the chance to turn this diamond in the rough into your dream home.
